companies.name: AhnLab, Inc.
companies.installProcedure:
**Set these after installation: **
1) Settings > Advanced Protection > Cloud Services > Enable Cloud-based Protection > Detection Sensitivity: Very Sensitive and enable Machine learning.

2) Settings > Scan Setting > Cleaning Action > If malware is detected: "Clean"

3) Settings > Scan Setting > Cleaning Action >  Infected compressed files: “Remove”

4) Settings > Scan Setting > Cleaning Action >  Potentially harmful programs: “Clean”

5) Settings >  Scan Exclusions > Add folder of file (C:\vb)
companies.updateProcedure: Click on the Update Button on GUI.
companies.log: Collect the log/data from test environment the product installed on following this instructions: 1) Run AhnReport (Windows Search > AhnReport > Run) 2) check options (AhnReport > Tools > AhnLab V3 Endpoint Security Debug Tracing, AhnLab ASD Engine debug tracing, and AhnLab Driver Debug Tracing), 3) Collect log/data (AhnReport > Report Product Error > Save)

incident_logs.title: Capture log stopped
incident_logs.detail: Capture log stopped with network error.
incident_logs.solution: Private network firewall was switched on.
